{{italic title}}

'''''Life''''', by David E. Sadava et al, is a 1983 [[biological science]] textbook, under continual revision, used at many [[colleges]] and [[universities]] around the [[United States of America]].<ref>{{cite book |title= Life: The Science of Biology |url= https://www.amazon.com/Life-science-biology-William-Purves/dp/0871507684 |date= 1983 |edition= 1st |pages= 1182 |isbn= 9780716798569 |first1= William K. |last1= Purves |publisher= W. Grant Press }}</ref> As of 2016, it is in its eleventh edition. It is published by [[W.H. Freeman]] through MacMillan Learning.

