This is a '''List of Serbian inventors and discoverers''', working locally or overseas. The list comprises people from Serbia and ethnic Serb people.
== Physics, mathematics and technology == *[[Ljubomir Klerić]], mathematical measuring tools *[[Mihailo Petrović]], *[[Voja Antonić]], computering; [[Galaksija (computer)|Galaksija]] home computer (1983). *[[Mihajlo Pupin]], [[Loading coil]] *[[Mihajlo Pupin Institute]], [[HRS-100]], [[CER Computers]], [[ATLAS-TIM AT 32]] *[[Nikola Tesla]], Induction motor, Contributions to the radio, Radio-controlled model, Remote control, Wireless power transfer, Tail-sitter, Conceptualized the smartphone, Plasma globe, Unmanned aerial vehicle, [[Beat Receiver|Beat receptor]], Capacitor discharge ignition, Magnifying transmitter, Teleforce, Telegeodynamics, Teleoperation, Tesla coil, Tesla turbine, Tesla's Egg of Columbus, Tesla's oscillator, Tesla valve, Three-phase electric power, Wardenclyffe tower, World Wireless System, Violet ray, Vacuum variable capacitor, Rotating magnetic field, Pioneered in alternating current research *[[Slobodan Ćuk]], [[Ćuk converter]] *[[Ivan Gutman]], [[Graph energy]], [[Matching polynomial]] *[[Ognjeslav Kostović Stepanović]] (1851–1916), "arbonite" (a type of [[plywood]]). *[[Jovan Karamata]], [[Karamata's inequality]], [[Karamata's notation]], [[Slowly varying function]] *[[Đuro Kurepa]], [[Kurepa tree]] *[[Bogdan Maglich]], [[Migma]] *[[Milutin Milanković]], [[Milankovitch cycles]], [[Revised Julian calendar]] *[[Tihomir Novakov]], [[black carbon]], [[aethalometer]] *[[Vlatko Verdal]], [[Quantum discord]] *[[Vladimir Vukićević]], [[webGL]], [[APNG]]
== Mechanics == *[[Nikola Bizumić]], [[hair clipper]] *[[Lazar the Serb]] ({{floruit}} 1404), invented and built the first known mechanical public clock in Russia. *[[Dobrivoje Božić]] (1885–1967), railway; inventor and constructor of the first [[railway air brake]]. *[[Miomir Vukobratović]], robotics; [[Powered exoskeleton]], [[Zero moment point]] *[[Rajko Tomović]], robotics; prostethic five-fingered hand
== Medicine and pharmacology == *[[Miodrag Radulovacki]], [[Andisone sleep theory]], pioneering pharmalogical studies for the treatment of sleep apnea.
